Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
The movie La Vita e Bella, is one of my favorite movies. it takes place in Italy during World War 2, and the main character is a jewish man who falls in love with an Italian Christian woman. He gets sent to a camp to be extermined along with their son, and all along he tries to pretend like it's a game so that his son does not get scared. The movie makes you appreciate life.